{"tid":126843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實30歲真的很尷尬，無論有工作還是沒有工作，問題仍然不少","createTime":"2017-02-19T16:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T16:04:09.000Z","uid":53000,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe3936417f8cd7f2320f339b32b318753a30e021","tid":126843,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:05:05.000Z","msg":"你踏入30歲了嗎？有人說20-30歲是人生最重要的10年，因為這個時候大學畢業，剛剛踏入社會，這10年就決定你餘下的人生路如何度過。可是到了30歲，是不是代表黃金10年已經過去呢？很多人覺得非常迷茫，不知道自己接下來應該幹甚麼。<br />\n<br />\n有工作的話就會覺得自己薪金不高，因為同年朋友有的已經經營生意中，有的則連續升職獲公司重用，自己被比下去。有女朋友/男朋友的人更迷茫，大家在一起足足7-10年了，這時候應該在事業上繼續努力衝刺，還是結婚造人呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果沒有穩定工作的人就會覺得自己失去動力，30歲被迫搬出來，不想再依靠父母。可是昂貴的租金及強積金令自己每個月變成月光族，沒有另一半的陪伴，生活特別難捱。身體開始變差，10年不斷地打工讓腰酸背痛的問題愈來愈嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n最重要是從前朋友道說聚就聚，要約出來非常容易。剛出來工作，大家每天下班都會約去飲酒聊天，「今日又比老闆話喇...」、「點呀你約到Venus出黎未...」，由工作談到溝女，再互相交換食女戰績，生活頗開心的。直到30歲要升職的已經天天加班，要做爸爸的亦已經成為家庭主夫，根本沒有時間坐在一起，更惶論飲酒吧。有時候想回家看看爸媽，驚覺他們已經在上年因癌症過世了......想找個人阿伴也是一件難事。"},{"pid":"95c24e7a5004877ed0fa11ff7876634986bc64ff","tid":126843,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76bd7f2be839392d8f32ff4f070ba4e05cead5b6","tid":126843,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"升中五了"},{"pid":"7422d9d1dabac67457ec86a2a67bf90d442e1bc9","tid":126843,"uid":41954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:44:11.000Z","msg":"毒撚十幾歲開始已經係咁"},{"pid":"6f077ea66d1ba81090fc5acd3d5ea9e27db7c291","tid":126843,"uid":65649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:52:43.000Z","msg":"經歷緊呢個階段，唔易捱，但都要過，希望40歲左右有份穩定合適既工作終老<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊努力吧"},{"pid":"3647e4f617c97ad68656b3f8c27609a8b74011f7","tid":126843,"uid":21378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:58:29.000Z","msg":"20-30歲是人生最重要的10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9868b92a74c7c996f92f2464de73982e94cfc0","tid":126843,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:02:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想死"},{"pid":"ada03a9e9f12f581ff79b8936fbcb8e362c87b18","tid":126843,"uid":53837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"香港生活真係好唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f617bdf6dc9c37dd8ca5b5c9e4c7060c09b1469","tid":126843,"uid":20552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a1c05b2c80497b66cf88995ef0b1b58859780a4","tid":126843,"uid":24335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0cc95dcb0e255481248d2bad616c1ee17338d5","tid":126843,"uid":30940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:07:04.000Z","msg":"呢十年都基本上決定左你之後30年係點過"},{"pid":"b15c5ab53d2b3fb915a53b622db07d22e79cc194","tid":126843,"uid":19196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:10:24.000Z","msg":"寫得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a206ded204c58c1ca36ff65a5665f10f856e02bc","tid":126843,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T18:06:49.000Z","msg":"三歲定八十la<br />\n洗等三十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324f92894066c80e58b22d6f42af523cc296c190","tid":126843,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T20:13:43.000Z","msg":"而家既人好長命，可能你到左四五十仲要養你父母"},{"pid":"4ebb36387c056006fe0b8bf327b37155ba7ec37d","tid":126843,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T20:20:02.000Z","msg":"//有時候想回家看看爸媽，驚覺他們已經在上年因癌症過世了......想找個人阿伴也是一件難事。//<br />\n<br />\n我仲讀緊書，但已經開始擔心呢樣&hellip;&hellip;我真係唔知當兩老離開時我會點&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"5144141bc11f8e6ad8ad024ad536d17934cf5d3f","tid":126843,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T20:56:43.000Z","msg":"人生得意需盡歡 莫使金樽空對月"},{"pid":"ac153691cdcfbd19946351c8c2a52c53aa15d217","tid":126843,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T21:03:57.000Z","msg":"係香港幾多歲都係咁折墜架啦<br />\n當你人工去到五萬<br />\n都係乜都要同人迫同人爭"},{"pid":"111c35bc50255ce0ae25602fe609f81175a6efb2","tid":126843,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T21:11:43.000Z","msg":"其實香港大部分人   係16~20歲人生走向已經決定左"},{"pid":"c3a9da4e83e59b62cac61a71ce1d82118bd39388","tid":126843,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T21:15:07.000Z","msg":"半同意<br />\n<br />\n我覺得男人20-30係去試唔同嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n30+ 就正式focus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24e0026383632f77bd8e97f65fa6fc9b4228f172","tid":126843,"uid":53000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半同意<br />\n<br />\n我覺得男人20-30係去試唔同嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n30+ 就正式focus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n30歲先起步就太遲啦，<br />\n3字頭先搵得萬一，萬二蚊，<br />\n除非你唔結婚唔生仔，<br />\n唔駛供養父母，唔駛買樓租樓而有地方住<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係，最遲27要起步，<br />\n當然你係有錢仔有父蔭既，<br />\n40歲唔起步都冇問題"},{"pid":"abe00d2e7a7d293c1bc5f4dbfb45f5f5316cc2f9","tid":126843,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2bfa3ea0be48602ef4de756ca24189c8db472f","tid":126843,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"正常香港人30歲已經有三層樓"},{"pid":"6a312262a4e707e6c672e60d809a53b8d27f4fb2","tid":126843,"uid":5289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T02